-----------Directory Structure-----------
/etc  All configs files
/home  Users Profiles
/usr   Softwares
/opt   optional 
/var   Logs (reports/troubleshooting)
/bin   binary All commands for normal user
/sbin  Super binary Administration Commands
/boot  kernel vmlinux
/lib  Kernel Modules
Kernel is the core part of OS    (OS kernel extension file  .dil

